WEBVTT

00:00:11.759 --> 00:00:13.160
Too coincidental.

00:00:13.599 --> 00:00:15.480
How could it all be such a coincidence?

00:00:16.039 --> 00:00:17.280
Is there anything else suspicious?

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:18.719
Look,

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:22.640
Luo Xiao, the day after the murder,

00:00:22.679 --> 00:00:24.960
showed up outside Feng Mao Company.

00:00:25.679 --> 00:00:27.760
And while on vacation, late at night,

00:00:28.199 --> 00:00:29.000
in the dead of night,

00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:31.000
he was wandering alone in the mountains.

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:33.079
Right in that exact same area,

00:00:33.159 --> 00:00:34.880
we found Chen Yongjiang's phone.

00:00:35.359 --> 00:00:36.520
And yet we still can't find

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:37.799
any trace of Chen Yongjiang.

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:40.719
Now, I just can't help but think...

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.399
that maybe Luo Xiao,

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:44.920
the day after the incident,

00:00:45.079 --> 00:00:47.679
went to Feng Mao Company, picked up Chen Yongjiang,

00:00:47.799 --> 00:00:49.479
and escorted him out of the city?

00:00:51.159 --> 00:00:52.600
But despite all these red flags,

00:00:52.759 --> 00:00:54.320
we don't have a single piece of direct evidence

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:56.399
that Luo Xiao helped Chen Yongjiang escape.

00:00:56.399 --> 00:00:57.159
Boss,

00:00:57.719 --> 00:00:59.079
But he's a lawyer.

00:00:59.159 --> 00:01:00.479
He obviously knows

00:01:00.719 --> 00:01:02.399
how to avoid suspicion.

00:01:02.479 --> 00:01:03.520
He's a lawyer,

00:01:03.679 --> 00:01:05.120
and he's got a family and a career.

00:01:05.319 --> 00:01:06.599
Chen Yongjiang committed murder, Boss.

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:07.400
It's a murder case.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.760
Why on earth would he get mixed up in this mess?

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:14.359
Anyway,

00:01:15.079 --> 00:01:16.799
if it's really like we suspect,

00:01:16.879 --> 00:01:18.599
that he helped Chen Yongjiang escape,

00:01:19.599 --> 00:01:20.760
it boils down to two things:

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:22.480
Either he was coerced,

00:01:22.799 --> 00:01:23.920
or he was bribed.

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:33.239
As for the sequence of the crime,

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:35.560
based on the clues we've gathered,

00:01:35.879 --> 00:01:37.599
the logic basically holds up.

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:40.719
But we lack any hard physical evidence.

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:42.840
First,

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:44.319
the waters where Luo Xiao vacationed

00:01:44.439 --> 00:01:45.560
are exactly where Chen Yongjiang's phone

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:46.959
was fished out.

00:01:47.519 --> 00:01:49.200
Since getting fired from the law firm,

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:51.439
Luo Xiao has remained in close contact

00:01:51.560 --> 00:01:53.719
with people tied to Feng Mao Company.

00:01:53.879 --> 00:01:54.799
Starting now,

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:56.280
I want the focus of this investigation

00:01:56.359 --> 00:01:57.239
to be solely on him.

00:01:57.319 --> 00:01:58.599
Lao Ma, run it through the system

00:01:58.680 --> 00:01:59.359
and pull up

00:01:59.439 --> 00:02:01.359
Luo Xiao's financial records

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:02.480
for the past month, and his movements.

00:02:02.560 --> 00:02:03.959
I want everything. Leave no blind spots.

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:04.599
Got it.

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:06.519
Zhao Dian, take a few guys

00:02:06.599 --> 00:02:08.400
and put Luo Xiao under 24-hour,

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:09.919
uninterrupted surveillance.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.039
Pay special attention to where he goes at night,

00:02:12.159 --> 00:02:13.319
and who he meets with in private.

00:02:13.759 --> 00:02:14.400
Xiao Ru,

00:02:14.599 --> 00:02:15.639
you handle the data compiling.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.039
Any comparisons, analyses,

00:02:18.159 --> 00:02:18.719
or anomalies,

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:20.039
report them to me immediately.

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:21.520
Jin Qiang,

00:02:21.639 --> 00:02:22.680
keep your team

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:24.879
combing through witness statements and evidence.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.479
Any tiny detail

00:02:26.599 --> 00:02:27.439
could very well

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:28.759
be our breakthrough.

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:29.639
Get to it.

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:42.960
Help!

00:02:43.719 --> 00:02:44.439
Help!

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:05.919
Boss,

00:03:06.199 --> 00:03:07.000
check please.

00:03:18.560 --> 00:03:19.400
Fifty-eight.

00:03:31.159 --> 00:03:31.960
Fifty-eight.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.639
What did Bro Mao say?

00:04:56.399 --> 00:04:58.600
Things are rocky inside and out right now,

00:04:58.959 --> 00:05:00.879
but the company still needs to operate.

00:05:01.399 --> 00:05:02.519
Bro Mao's intention is

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:03.759
for me to organize the brothers

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:04.959
and stabilize the situation first.

00:05:05.399 --> 00:05:07.120
I handle the money, you do the laundering.

00:05:07.399 --> 00:05:08.439
Same as before.

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:25.199
This money...

00:05:26.839 --> 00:05:27.680
has a smell to it.

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.079
Well, it's money.

00:05:30.560 --> 00:05:32.199
Of course it smells like money.

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:38.800
This money...

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:40.519
can be laundered in about two or three days.

00:05:42.480 --> 00:05:43.199
That fast?

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:44.560
Spoken like an amateur.

00:05:47.519 --> 00:05:48.360
This money...

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:50.240
we first split it among various proxies.

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:52.240
That way the boys can handle it.

00:05:53.439 --> 00:05:54.519
They wire it into cards in batches.

00:05:54.759 --> 00:05:55.920
Once it's in the banking system,

00:05:56.079 --> 00:05:57.839
this money looks completely clean.

00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:59.319
But that's only step one.

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:00.920
Next,

00:06:01.319 --> 00:06:02.120
each proxy...

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:04.240
gets a loan on a micro-loan platform.

00:06:04.639 --> 00:06:05.720
Once the loan hits the account,

00:06:06.399 --> 00:06:07.639
it gets wired under various pretexts

00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:08.839
to our Front company,

00:06:08.920 --> 00:06:10.160
Shengquan International Trade.

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.199
Four twos.

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:21.600
Pay up, pay up. Come on.

00:06:26.959 --> 00:06:28.480
On the surface, its business seems broad,

00:06:28.639 --> 00:06:30.560
but it's really our money laundering shell.

00:06:31.319 --> 00:06:32.720
After Shengquan receives the money,

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:33.839
depending on the contract size,

00:06:33.920 --> 00:06:35.160
it kicks back a service fee to us,

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:36.240
or something along those lines.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:37.920
A round trip like this,

00:06:37.959 --> 00:06:39.319
takes about two or three days.

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:40.879
As for losses and cuts,

00:06:41.279 --> 00:06:41.920
a quarter,

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:42.879
around 25 percent.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:44.120
That's all considered normal overhead.

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:54.160
Datou,

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:57.199
why hasn't that money hit the account yet?

00:06:57.560 --> 00:06:58.759
The money's already with A Min.

00:06:58.959 --> 00:07:00.279
I called him this morning,

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:01.600
but no one picked up.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:04.000
I'll go pay him a visit later.

00:07:04.199 --> 00:07:04.959
A Min...

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:07.040
You didn't know?

00:07:07.519 --> 00:07:09.199
Shengquan was set up in his name.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.560
If there's any word from Bro Mao,

00:07:12.680 --> 00:07:14.240
you know what to do, right?

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:17.480
So...

00:07:17.879 --> 00:07:20.399
on the surface he has no ties to Feng Mao,

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:22.319
so the cops can't trace him to it, right?

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:23.160
Right.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:24.560
Otherwise, how would the money move?

00:07:24.839 --> 00:07:26.000
Do I really need to spell it out for you?

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:28.959
Here's the deal.

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:31.399
Datou, no need for you to look for him.

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:33.639
In Bro Mao's name,

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:34.920
call a general meeting.

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:36.000
Everyone has to be there,

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:36.839
including A Min.

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:37.920
The meeting?

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:39.600
Are you coming?

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:40.920
I'm the Business Consultant.

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:42.040
Of course I'm going.

00:07:42.519 --> 00:07:43.319
When?

00:07:45.879 --> 00:07:46.560
Tonight.

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:53.399
We're discussing something this serious,

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:56.000
couldn't we pick a proper place?

00:07:57.079 --> 00:07:58.120
Does it really have to be here?

00:07:59.199 --> 00:08:00.920
What, you want the cops to listen in?

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:03.199
These are all our own businesses.

00:08:03.839 --> 00:08:04.600
It's safe.

00:08:06.279 --> 00:08:07.120
Besides,

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:08.399
the two of us running around all day,

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:09.800
so we came for a foot soak

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:10.600
to unwind a bit.

00:08:31.519 --> 00:08:32.399
Having a meeting...

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:34.960
This comfortable?

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:42.879
Lawyer Luo,

00:08:44.679 --> 00:08:45.759
Haven't seen you in a few days.

00:08:46.559 --> 00:08:48.000
I should be calling you...

00:08:48.840 --> 00:08:50.120
Bro Xiao now, shouldn't I?

00:08:58.679 --> 00:08:59.799
Where's Bro Mao?

00:09:00.360 --> 00:09:01.840
He just asked me to step in temporarily

00:09:01.879 --> 00:09:02.919
to coordinate the company's business.

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:05.080
After all,

00:09:05.399 --> 00:09:06.799
the brothers still gotta eat, right?

00:09:07.039 --> 00:09:07.799
Right?

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:13.440
Datou,

00:09:14.399 --> 00:09:15.759
how exactly did Bro Mao tell Lawyer Luo

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:17.240
to coordinate things?

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:30.320
This is Bro Mao's signature and fingerprint.

00:09:30.960 --> 00:09:32.360
If you don't believe me,

00:09:33.559 --> 00:09:34.679
you can verify it yourself.

00:09:39.639 --> 00:09:41.240
Can Bro Mao even read?

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.240
Datou,

00:09:43.559 --> 00:09:45.600
tell me, where's our contract,

00:09:45.759 --> 00:09:46.960
our agreement?

00:09:51.559 --> 00:09:52.320
Well...

00:09:55.919 --> 00:09:57.320
Whether you believe it or not,

00:09:57.519 --> 00:09:59.159
this is what Bro Mao wants.

00:09:59.639 --> 00:10:01.840
The situation right now is indeed quite unique.

00:10:02.360 --> 00:10:03.840
That's why Bro Mao had me

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:06.000
risk arrest to withdraw the money.

00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:08.279
The brothers still gotta eat, don't they?

00:10:09.080 --> 00:10:10.679
You're holding back the money right now?

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:12.879
You trying to hog it all?

00:10:14.039 --> 00:10:15.080
I've been with Bro Mao for years.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:16.799
Do I need you here trying to stir the pot?

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:18.759
Now that Bro Mao is gone,

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:20.480
as his brother,

00:10:20.679 --> 00:10:23.200
I should be guarding his business for him.

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:25.759
Even if he needs someone to take over,

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:28.080
it won't be an outsider like you.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:33.600
I'll put it straight right here, today.

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:35.320
When Bro Mao shows his face,

00:10:35.720 --> 00:10:36.919
the money shows up.

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:40.200
In this current situation,

00:10:40.279 --> 00:10:41.759
the cops have their eyes all over Bro Mao.

00:10:42.559 --> 00:10:43.919
And you want him to show his face now?

00:10:44.360 --> 00:10:45.480
Do you just want him dead?

00:10:45.759 --> 00:10:46.720
Say that again?

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:49.039
What the hell are you trying to do?

00:10:50.960 --> 00:10:52.240
Brought a few boys, think you're tough, huh?

00:10:56.279 --> 00:10:58.080
The cops are on high alert out there.

00:10:58.759 --> 00:11:00.240
Bro Mao only gave him the money

00:11:00.879 --> 00:11:02.200
because he trusted him!

00:11:04.799 --> 00:11:06.559
Did Bro Mao give him the money,

00:11:07.879 --> 00:11:09.960
or did he snatch Bro Mao's money?

00:11:21.039 --> 00:11:21.919
Three days.

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:24.879
Three days from now,

00:11:26.799 --> 00:11:27.840
Bro Mao shows up.

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:36.440
Fine.

00:11:37.240 --> 00:11:38.200
Three days.

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:44.960
Three days.

00:11:45.679 --> 00:11:46.399
Let's go.

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:16.759
Boss Tian,

00:12:17.039 --> 00:12:19.360
this gorgeous place is really mine?

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:28.639
You're really giving it to me?

00:12:28.840 --> 00:12:29.639
Do you like it?

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.639
I absolutely love it.

00:12:31.960 --> 00:12:32.919
Do you want it?

00:12:34.919 --> 00:12:35.759
I want it.

00:12:37.159 --> 00:12:38.000
Oh, stop it.

00:12:38.559 --> 00:12:41.240
Whatever I promised you, you'll get.

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:45.279
I knew it.

00:12:45.759 --> 00:12:46.919
Boss Tian is the absolute

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:48.440
best to me.

00:12:52.080 --> 00:12:52.799
Ganzi,

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:54.679
do you know Sun Wukong's surname?

00:12:54.799 --> 00:12:55.759
It's Sun, obviously.

00:12:56.159 --> 00:12:57.200
You really have no clue.

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:00.159
Many years ago,

00:13:00.759 --> 00:13:02.000
there was a great flood.

00:13:02.639 --> 00:13:03.559
Then there was this guy called Da Yu.

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:04.639
He was taming the flood, right?

00:13:04.759 --> 00:13:06.440
Using that magic sea-calming staff.

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:09.039
Spent years but couldn't fix it, you know?

00:13:09.480 --> 00:13:10.399
So what about his wife?

00:13:10.519 --> 00:13:11.639
She was waiting for him at home.

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:12.720
Just waiting and waiting...

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:14.200
She waited until she turned into a stone.

00:13:14.759 --> 00:13:16.159
Where did Sun Wukong pop out from?

00:13:16.799 --> 00:13:17.679
From a stone.

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:19.679
So what is Sun Wukong's surname?

00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:20.600
Shi, for "stone."

00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:22.759
It's Da.

00:13:23.399 --> 00:13:24.679
Da Yu is his father.

00:13:25.240 --> 00:13:26.159
The "Da" from Da Yu.

00:13:28.120 --> 00:13:29.519
No wonder he's called Great Sage.

00:13:29.679 --> 00:13:30.559
Right, Great Sage.

00:13:30.639 --> 00:13:31.559
It all connects now, doesn't it?

00:13:31.639 --> 00:13:32.639
Great Sage.

00:13:33.519 --> 00:13:34.480
Great Sage.

00:13:34.679 --> 00:13:35.399
Exactly.

00:13:35.559 --> 00:13:37.559
No wonder it's "Da." Great Sage.

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:39.960
Bro Yao,

00:13:40.840 --> 00:13:42.320
how come this door's open?

00:13:44.559 --> 00:13:45.600
They must be here.

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:47.120
Time to get to work.

00:14:40.600 --> 00:14:41.799
What the hell are you doing?

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:43.679
How many times do I have to tell you?

00:14:43.759 --> 00:14:44.960
Don't get that on me!

00:14:45.039 --> 00:14:46.320
You're gonna ruin my clothes again.

00:14:47.320 --> 00:14:48.399
You just won't stop, will you?

00:14:51.559 --> 00:14:52.480
Bro Yao.

00:14:53.679 --> 00:14:55.879
He is the Great Sage Equalling Heaven.

00:14:55.879 --> 00:14:57.399
Shouldn't his surname be Qi?

00:14:58.600 --> 00:14:59.559
Which "Qi"?

00:15:00.559 --> 00:15:02.360
He was only Great Sage for seven days.

00:15:03.559 --> 00:15:04.480
Seven days.

00:15:04.600 --> 00:15:05.480
"Seven-Day" Great Sage.

00:15:05.480 --> 00:15:06.799
That "seven days" Qi.

00:15:07.080 --> 00:15:07.879
What else?

00:15:20.879 --> 00:15:21.679
Boss.

00:15:22.559 --> 00:15:23.960
Was it really as messed up as you say?

00:15:25.159 --> 00:15:25.960
That?

00:15:26.519 --> 00:15:27.879
I'm actually holding back.

00:15:28.480 --> 00:15:30.240
If you had been at the scene back then,

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:31.639
you'd have puked all over your shoes.

00:15:35.320 --> 00:15:37.039
The 0301 Dismemberment Case.

00:15:37.759 --> 00:15:39.120
Chopped and hacked to pieces.

00:15:39.919 --> 00:15:41.600
Couldn't even pull a single fingerprint.

00:15:41.960 --> 00:15:43.679
When we got to the scene back then,

00:15:43.799 --> 00:15:44.639
the body

00:15:44.799 --> 00:15:46.159
was chopped into 42 pieces.

00:15:46.879 --> 00:15:48.919
The blood and bits of flesh

00:15:48.919 --> 00:15:50.639
splattered all over the walls...

00:15:52.279 --> 00:15:53.399
Let me put it this way,

00:15:53.639 --> 00:15:55.519
our whole team ate vegetarian for a month.

00:15:57.159 --> 00:15:57.919
And then what?

00:15:58.120 --> 00:15:59.200
Absolutely nothing.

00:16:01.240 --> 00:16:02.399
We extracted DNA,

00:16:02.919 --> 00:16:04.039
but back then,

00:16:04.240 --> 00:16:05.679
our database was too small.

00:16:05.960 --> 00:16:07.080
It yielded no match.

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:09.360
Even after a few system upgrades,

00:16:09.519 --> 00:16:10.879
we made a special trip each time

00:16:10.879 --> 00:16:11.720
to run the comparison again.

00:16:12.159 --> 00:16:13.240
But still, absolutely nothing.

00:16:13.960 --> 00:16:15.279
Just like the Xin Qili case.

00:16:16.639 --> 00:16:17.559
I'm telling you,

00:16:17.919 --> 00:16:18.759
the Xin Qili case

00:16:18.960 --> 00:16:19.759
might just be

00:16:20.559 --> 00:16:22.519
the key to cracking

00:16:22.879 --> 00:16:23.600
the 0301 Dismemberment Case.

00:16:24.399 --> 00:16:25.639
Here's my number.

00:16:25.879 --> 00:16:26.919
If you happen to recall anything

00:16:26.960 --> 00:16:28.480
at all about Xin Qili,

00:16:28.600 --> 00:16:29.720
give me a call anytime.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:31.039
Okay, okay, okay.

00:16:31.159 --> 00:16:32.279
If there's nothing else, I'll be heading out.

00:16:32.279 --> 00:16:32.759
Sure.

00:16:32.840 --> 00:16:33.519
Sorry for the trouble.

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:34.720
No problem at all.

00:16:34.799 --> 00:16:35.559
Okay, thanks.

00:16:35.720 --> 00:16:36.440
You're welcome.

00:16:36.720 --> 00:16:37.960
This is so bizarre.

00:16:38.200 --> 00:16:39.679
Between Xin Qili and Chen Yongjiang,

00:16:39.759 --> 00:16:40.799
their only connection

00:16:40.799 --> 00:16:42.600
is Shi Qijun from Feng Mao Company.

00:16:43.399 --> 00:16:44.440
He once paid Xin Qili

00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:45.679
a small labor-related loan.

00:16:46.200 --> 00:16:48.000
But as for Xin Qili and Chen Yongjiang,

00:16:48.120 --> 00:16:49.240
there were no financial disputes

00:16:49.240 --> 00:16:50.639
or personal ties whatsoever.

00:16:51.639 --> 00:16:53.480
So what exactly is his motive for murder?

00:16:54.440 --> 00:16:56.639
We can't say they had zero contact.

00:16:56.720 --> 00:16:59.200
After all, Xin Qili only took odd jobs

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:01.360
that left no trace.

00:17:01.919 --> 00:17:03.639
Trying to trace his social circle

00:17:03.639 --> 00:17:04.960
really isn't easy.

00:17:07.279 --> 00:17:09.000
I found this under a pillow in the back.

00:17:10.920 --> 00:17:11.960
What is this?

00:17:13.240 --> 00:17:14.039
Let me see.

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:17.960
It's a fortune slip.

00:17:18.759 --> 00:17:20.680
"Sickness swept away, returning by crane."

00:17:21.519 --> 00:17:23.119
Xin Qili must've drawn it for his sister.

00:17:24.680 --> 00:17:26.640
So it's a fortune slip for recovery.

00:17:26.640 --> 00:17:27.920
So why is it half-burned?

00:17:30.079 --> 00:17:31.559
This auspicious cloud pattern...

00:17:33.599 --> 00:17:35.039
This slip was drawn at the Great Sage Temple.

00:17:54.079 --> 00:17:54.960
Hello, Master.

00:17:55.920 --> 00:17:56.640
Hello.

00:17:57.079 --> 00:17:58.440
Excuse me, is this from your temple?

00:17:59.640 --> 00:18:00.400
Yes.

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:01.400
What's the matter?

00:18:02.119 --> 00:18:04.079
Do you have any recollection of this slip?

00:18:05.720 --> 00:18:06.680
Let me see.

00:18:15.039 --> 00:18:16.680
What recollection are you asking about?

00:18:17.559 --> 00:18:18.759
First, the one who drew it.

00:18:19.079 --> 00:18:21.359
Second, why it was burned halfway,

00:18:21.799 --> 00:18:22.720
yet kept like this.

00:18:22.839 --> 00:18:24.279
Is there any special meaning to that?

00:18:27.240 --> 00:18:28.440
I am getting old.

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:31.039
In this temple,

00:18:32.279 --> 00:18:33.440
fates come and go.

00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:36.200
This old lamp of mine only provides light.

00:18:36.559 --> 00:18:38.200
It never asks where they come from or go.

00:18:39.240 --> 00:18:40.200
This fortune slip

00:18:40.359 --> 00:18:41.359
is what one seeks.

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:43.160
To seek is to form an attachment.

00:18:43.920 --> 00:18:45.200
Burning the slip

00:18:45.559 --> 00:18:46.599
means the seeker

00:18:47.079 --> 00:18:48.759
has let go of their inner attachment.

00:18:49.960 --> 00:18:51.279
Since half of it remains,

00:18:52.200 --> 00:18:53.519
the attachment is not fully severed.

00:19:00.880 --> 00:19:01.559
Alright.

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:02.759
Thank you.